				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">ND or CA?<a name="24203"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 27 04 2:41 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I was just wondering if it would be better to get ND or CA first?
<br />

<br />
I also wonder about how ND works. Description says: &quot;Increases the player’s base hitpoints. (The percentages are based off your base hitpoints, which include stamina and stamina effects.)&quot; What I'm not sure of is which HP the percentage are based off? I would greatly appreciate if someone could explain it to me<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
I am lvl 65, have run3, regen3, MC1, FM so far. I both raid and group, don't solo very much. When grouping I tend to pull, but not in raids though. The content we are raiding atm is NToV, and lower PoP. 
<br />

<br />
Hugs Miriel
