				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: ND or CA?<a name="24205"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 27 04 3:09 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>ND adds a percentage to your unbuffed HPs.
<br />

<br />
Your Magelo shows 2952 HPs. That's the amount ND is calculated upon So ND1 would add about 59 HP, ND3 295 HPs.
<br />

<br />
Now, usually I personally would suggest CA over ND, but if you really do a lot NToV currently, then ND might be superior.
<br />
If you have more HPs you have a higher chance to survive those AEs.
<br />
If you pull lot for exp-groups, then CA would be better. I simply think that avoiding a few nasty hits is better than having 300 HPs more here.
<br />

<br />
Well...up to you ;-)
<br />
</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
