			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>ND would be the greatest benefit.  The HP bonus from ND 1-3 is probably the best payoff for points spent on archetype AAs for bards, period.  I strongly endorse CA too, but ND is just more valuable in the long run.  CA won't help you survive spell effects, too.  I know Keiz is a huge fan of CF and SCF -- personally I still think they are more eye candy than actual DPS increase, but to each his own.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />  When it comes down to bang for the buck -- benefit per AA -- ND is the best of the archetypes, if you ask me.</span></td>
