				<td colspan="2"><span>didn't want to argue at first, since everyone shall know what he wants, but since I wante to add a nice augment to my gear anyway I took some figures....
<br />

<br />
HPs with an empty slot 1 on bp: 4279.
<br />
HPs after adding a 30 HP/mana-augment (Gem of bolstered Power) into that slot: 4313.
<br />

<br />
4313 - 4279 = 34
<br />
34 = 30? huh?
<br />

<br />
34/30 =1,133333
<br />
= +13,3%
<br />

<br />
now explain that please ;-)
<br />

<br />
My explanation:
<br />
ND3+PE adds 12% to RAW HP gear as well.
<br />
12% of 30 are 3.6 HPs.
<br />
