				<td colspan="2"><span>ND3 and PE do affect pure hp gear.  As stated above, a 100 raw hp upgrade, with no change in stam will increase your hps by 112.
<br />

<br />
As far as which to get first?  I did ND 1, 2, 3 soon as i had my 6 general AAs in, and have never regretted it.  I then did singing mastery 1, instrument mastery 1, pe, then added one level to each of CA and CS.  In all honesty, i dont think I started working seriously on CA and CS until i was 140+ AA range.
<br />

<br />
I did not take the normal path that many did with my AAs, but have been happy with my progression.  All in all, if I was doing it again, I would pick up ND3 and PE first, then go back and do CA/CS, though I see the arguments for both directions.</span></td>
